Requirements
------------
 * ghc 6.4
 * libgmp (for ghc)
 * wxhaskell 0.9.4 (requires Unicode patch: see below)
 * wxWidgets 2.5 or 2.6 (for wxhaskell)
 * alex 2.0.1
 * happy 1.14 and up
 * graphviz (for GUI) 

wxWidgets and wxhaskell
-----------------------
For the moment, you'll need to compile wxWidgets and wxhaskell with special 
options.  Please see
  http://wiki.loria.fr/wiki/GenI/Getting_GenI

Building geni
-------------
 ./configure
 make 
 make install

(Note: blind users or GUI abstainers can do 'make nogui' 
 instead of just 'make')
